                                    <strong>Upozorenje:</strong> ovaj korak ne možete poništiti. <br><br>
                                    <strong>Savjet:</strong> ako se time promijene dijelovi predloga na koje Utiču drugi amandmani, doći će do konflikta. U tom slučaju morate ručno urediti sudarne amandmane.', // Original: Once the changes of this amendment are adopted, a new version of the motion including these changes is created. The original version and this amendment will be kept for reference.<br><br>                                     <strong>Warning:</strong> you can not undo this step.<br><br>                                     <strong>Hint:</strong> if this changes parts of the motion that are affected by other amendments, a collision will occur. In this case, you need to manual edit the colliding amendments.
